Package: sportreandva
Title: A Tool for Analyzing Reliability and Validity in Sports Science
Version: 2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Ruiqi",
           family = "Cheng",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "crq1477@163.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-5688-6245"))
Description: Provides a focused suite of functions to conduct comprehensive 
    reliability and analysis for repeated measures data in sports science. 
    All functions are designed to work with long-format data. 
    Key functions include reliability analysis for two sessions (t-test) or 
    multiple sessions (ANOVA) and validity analysis, as well as Bland-Altman analysis and visualization.
    In addition, this package also supports exporting publication-ready three-line tables.
